{"tid":1738961,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論]召集和理非打經濟戰 和你撳","createTime":"2019-11-19T11:59:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T17:23:40.000Z","uid":95234,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"257e06e241a4a518dc8bad157a0b47283f05a169","tid":1738961,"uid":95234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:59:30.000Z","msg":"經濟明明就係政府大大個春袋<br />\n8月大家兌完美金之後就再冇活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二百萬人一齊做同一樣野根本就好大威力<br />\n<br />\n不如發起搞和你撳<br />\n全港和理非係同一日 一齊落街排隊撳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 手持現金 減低銀行存款</span></span><br />\n8月大家一齊撳錢手持現金 港元存款跌1110億<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 人人排隊撳錢 製造擠提現象</span></span><br />\n嚇死藍絲廢老 爭住撳錢 形成雪球效應<br />\n擠提影響社會經濟活動 增加政府壓力<br />\n<br />\n最重要既係 排隊撳錢唔犯法<br />\n岩哂和理非<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點唔係撳幾多錢<br />\n而係排隊 只要夠多人 人人都會驚</span></span><br />\n各位和理非排龍門排黃店又肯排 曬少少時間排atm抗爭都得掛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇有經驗既活動搞手<br />\n同埋文宣組煲大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 討論緊係美國撳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389eea29936c3ebc02fc5a26edc151fce3e540b8","tid":1738961,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:04:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\n【行動】Twitter 戰線：世界各地政要火力全開！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqrTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=dd4ea103\" data-auto-link targe